Beta Development started on May 5th, 2025
Beta released on June 1st, 2025

13 major updates (Forgot to document them. Oops.), adding a second sub, menus, a new sound effect engine, etc.

u0.2025.34.1, 28/8/2025
  Music
    Replaced all copyrighted and/or placeholder songs in the template soundtrack with royalty-free songs by Scott Buckley and Chris Zabriskie

u0.2025.34.2, 31/8/2025
  UI
    Added a background to the pause menu

u0.2025.37.1, 17/9/2025
  UI
    Added a mobile slider to the main and pause menu
    Added a settings button that opens and closes the pause menu
    Added a joystick and 3 buttons that control movement, light setting, and light direction on mobile
  Music
    Replaced Cylinder One by Chris Zabriskie with Undertow by Scott Buckley

u0.2025.37.2, 20/9/25
  Music
    Replaced Cylinder Five by Chris Zabriskie with The Things That Keep Us Here by Scott Buckley
    Replaced The Restoration by Scott Buckley with The Exodus by Scott Buckley

u1.2025.41.1, 15/10/2025
  Released the finished Scratch version

u2 development started on October 15th, 2025

u1.2025.42.1, 19/10/2025
  Music
    Replaced Cylinder Eight by Chris Zabriskie with The Great Sea by Scott Buckley
  Switched to a new update version format

u2.2025.43.1, 2/11/2025
  v2 Game
    The v2 game has been finished! Some final edits are being made and the game should be released today or tomorrow!

u2.2025.43.2, 2/11/2025
  v2 Game
    The v2 game has been released! https://mehonje.itch.io/challenger-deep
    It's to big to upload onto Github, so I now have an Itch account.

u2.2025.43.2, 4/11/2025
  v2 Game
    Glowing dots have been added and can be found below 200m

u2.2025.44.1, 5/11/2025
  v1 Game
    Added Elijah_2028 the the list of winners! Congratulations!
    Saving/Loading
      Made saving and loading store and restore the timer that counts how long you have played

u2.2025.44.2, 5/11/2025
  v2 Game
    UI
      Added delete buttons to game slot button that clear a save's data. THEY CURRENTLY DO NOT PROMPT FOR CONFIRMATION!
    Bugfixes
      Fixed a bug where "Game1", "Game2", and "Game3" jsons were not created if they didn't exist or if the "games" folder didn't exist
      Fixed a bug where the game would crash if a game json didn't exist
      Fixed a bug where the game slot button darkened the text of the button

u2.2025.44.3, 6/11/2025
  v1 Game
    Saving/Loading
      Added encryption to the save codes to make cheating more difficult
    Fixed a bug where the glowing dots found below 200m would form a line of dots if the player went faster that 360 m/s

u2.2025.44.4, 7/11/2025
  v1 Game
    Saving/Loading
      Replaced the binary encryption added in v2.2025.44.3 with hex encryption

u2.2025.44.5, 9/11/2025
  v1 Game
    Saving/Loading
      Added a large buffer at the beginning of save codes
  v2 Game
    Added functionality to the temperature gauge in the bottom-left of the screen

u2.2025.45.1, 16/11/2025
  v1 Game
