u2.2026.0.1, 2/1/2026
  v2 Game
    Applied changes made to v1 game in u2.2025.52.1
    Bugfixes
      Fixed a bug where save data was not loaded if it was empty
      Fixed a bug where save files were not created if they didn't exist
      Fixed a bug where a crash could occur if save data was incorrectly formatted
      Fixed a bug where a crash could occur if the save file failed to open
      Fixed a bug where a crash could occur if the save data failed to load
  Changed update format slightly
